  <h1>
    <div class="book-me">
      <a class="btn btn-lg" href="/contact">Contact us</a>
    </div>
    <span class="hello">
      Welcome to GPS-Robotic,
      <small><em>wir sprechen auch <a href="/fr/" rel="alternate" hreflang="fr">deutsch</a> !</em></small>
    </span>
  </h1>

  <p>
    This page belongs to the advanced internship "GPS on wheels" of the 
	<a href="http://joanna.iwr.uni-heidelberg.de/rlab/de/home">Robotics lab Heidelberg</a>
	at the Interdisciplinary Center for Scientific Computing (IWR). The aim of this internship 
	is the construction of an autonomous model car controlled by an 
	<a href="http://www.raspberrypi.org/">Raspberry Pi</a> and guided by GPS data.
	The internship involves the construction of the hardware parts like the car, the steering via 
	Raspberry as well as the development of appropriate algorithms.
  </p>

  <p><img src="images/ReelyBlaze.jpg" alt="Our model car." title="Our model car: The Reely Blaze"></p>	

